{"sections":{"ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16177341137065__ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"{{ article.metafields.custom.title_image.value }}"}}},"block_order":["template--16177341137065__ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33-image-1"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":false,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"left","media_width":"6","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"","title":"<p>{{ article.title }}<\/p>","description":"{{ article.metafields.custom.paragraph_1 | metafield_tag }}","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"3ebc68a8-39a5-4ef0-96ec-3daf87a7a4fc":{"type":"seo-copy","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","content_intro":"<p><strong>DO: BUY WHAT YOU LOVE<\/strong><\/p><p><em>Natalie: <\/em>Simply, a piece of vintage jewellery should be chosen because it resonates with you, and because you fall in love with it. Not only are they imbued with the histories and stories of their past owners, but vintage jewellery also provides an opportunity to embrace sustainable purchasing habits – offering once-cherished designs a second (or third) lease on life.<\/p><p>I have always had a love for vintage jewellery, or vintage anything really. I used to spend hours in op shops collecting all sorts of odd finds – furniture, clothes, hats, even once a vintage suitcase which I used to transport and display my first ever collection! I love the mystery and enigmatic nature of vintage pieces, the opportunity for speculation on their history and journey. I also have a deep reverence for the incredible craftsmanship many of these piece’s hold. So much tradition and heritage exists in every tiny detail, which is where my love for vintage jewellery originates from.<\/p><p>I encourage you to find your spark. Is it a particular stone colour or cut, the setting or design style or maybe even the piece’s provenance and era that speaks to you? Is it because it reminds you of a place, someone special or loved ones from generations past? I always like to remind clients that jewellery doesn’t have to be engraved or marked with a special stone to become solely yours – it can be anything about the piece that sparks a feeling or takes you back to a moment in time.<\/p><p>There’s a sense of romance and allure inherit in vintage pieces, and finding the perfect design should feel akin to falling in love: a lightning bolt of recognition; the sense that you two were destined to be connected.<\/p>","content":""}},"22942553-01da-4697-89ac-f500b502883f":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"template--16177341137065__22942553-01da-4697-89ac-f500b502883f-image-3":{"type":"image","settings":{"apply_overlay":false,"devices":"mobile_desktop","content_position":"underLeft","subheading":"","title":"","description":"{{ article.metafields.custom.paragraph_2 | metafield_tag }}","description_mobile":"{{ article.metafields.custom.paragraph_2 | metafield_tag }}","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_metaobject":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_3_metaobject":"","button_3_text":"","button_3_link":"","button_style":"underline","include_no_media_border":false,"metaobject_autoplay":"","metaobject_loop":"","metaobject_apply_overlay":"","metaobject_content_position":"","metaobject_colour_style":"","metaobject_button_style":"","metaobject_devices":""}}},"block_order":["template--16177341137065__22942553-01da-4697-89ac-f500b502883f-image-3"],"settings":{"grid_items_count":3,"grid_items_count_pocket":"1\/2","text_align":"center","subheading":"","title":"","description":"","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"fe4a59da-74f2-4522-93d1-709dd4b43c45":{"type":"content-list","blocks":{"template--161773411370